data.title: Mike Herrera of Washington Pop Punk Group MxPx Calls Dallas His "Second Home"
data.meta_description: There was a time when pop-punk trio MxPx toured constantly, and hit Dallas on every go-round. Whether it was Deep Ellum Live or Trees, the gaps between shows were short. But these days the Washington-based band doesn't tour at all, instead opting to restrict their travel to weekends and visit a new destination every few months. This weekend it's Dallas.
